  [2]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jakarta_Servlet
  [3]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jakarta_EE
  [4]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GlassFish
  [5]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apache_Tomcat

